platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Find great deals with Watch List

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Gathering the dozens of weekly promotional flyers and coupon books from every store in your area would take forever, not to mention that it’d cost the lives of many innocent trees. Flipp automatically collects advertised offers from local stores and online retailers, letting you flip through perfect digital copies of flyers to circle items you’re interested in or clip virtual coupons for hundreds of products. It’s an intelligent and indispensable shopping companion that saves time, money, and plenty of paper.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Save time and money with deals and coupons at your fingertips.
